messages.messageBody:
2/28/03 17:45:

> Today is my
> un-birthday. I am a leapyear baby, and even though I have been alive 31
> calendar years, I get denied having a birthday today.

Happy Birthday, Ang. Have a great party from 11p.m. to 1 a.m. or something
like that.

My piano professor, also a leap year baby, had his 16th actual birthday when
I was in school. We all gave him a hard time about being "sweet sixteen and
never been kissed". All the funnier because he was such an obnoxious flirt!

So you have more more year of being 7, huh? :)

brenda
